                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A troll polyp\u2019s slam splatters regenerating biomass onto that target. The target must succeed at a DC 12 Reflex saving throw (DC 14 if the troll polyp scored a critical hit) or become entangled until it escapes by succeeding at a DC 15 Acrobatics or Athletics check made as a move action. The biomass also releases its target if the mass takes 5 damage from one attack (AC 10).",
