                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A troll polyp\u2019s regeneration stops functioning for 1 round only if the polyp takes simultaneous damage from more than one energy damage type during the same turn or takes damage of three or more energy types in a given round. If one foe readies an action to attack the polyp when another foe does, the two attacks are treated as occurring on the same turn for this ability\u2019s purposes.",
                "name": "Versatile Regeneration",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
